  "title": "Echo Block",
  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Echo Block</b> is a type of <linked>block</linked> which turns completely invisible once placed. It is sold by the <linked>Cyborg</linked> NPC for <span class=\"coin\" title=\"10 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"1000\"><span class=\"sc\">10</span></span> when he is spoken to in a <linked>Graveyard</linked>. Once placed, the Echo Block cannot be seen by the player unless they have the <linked>Spectre Goggles</linked> equipped or are near an <linked>Echo Chamber</linked>.",
    "Despite their invisibility, Echo Blocks retain the properties of normal blocks and can thus be <linked>hammered</linked>, actuated with an <linked>Actuator</linked>, stood and <linked>grappled</linked> on, used to <linked>hoik</linked>, and mined with any <linked>pickaxe</linked> or <linked>drill</linked>."
